A short time ago, we introduced a new hiring process utilizing the Position Request Form.  The idea is to complete the form and get the required approvals before beginning the recruitment process.  However, I do understand there may be times when we need to "slam dunk" a new hire and we'll make sure we do our best to not be a barrier to your hiring/recruiting needs.

However, please bear in mind that the forms contain salary information and we need to ensure that they remain secure.  Any requisition forms that require approval should be directed to me either through Confidential interoffice mail, secured fax (974-6985) or secured email (Dawn.Doucet@enron.com).  I will forward all requests to Rob Milnthorp for approval.

I've revised the form (slightly)....

 
It will also be available on the Enron Canada HR website:  http://hrweb.enron.com/ect/

Thanks.....